Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:38.70,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}来るのなら　信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:35.99,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fs48}（来るときを）
