Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:06.42,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}不要用语言让我生出幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:10.59,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我无须你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.09,0:22:15.30,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}凛冽的寒风把我的心冻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:19.68,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}眼里燃烧着誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:28.44,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}现在你我心照不宣  只需奋力奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:33.44,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}接受彼此一切的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:38.70,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}若是会到来  我坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:35.99,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fs57}（一定会到来）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:44.21,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}悲伤穿梭于整个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:48.25,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}让我们牢记这段记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:53.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}想要触摸彼此心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.47,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}即使擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:23:01.97,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}也要追逐同一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:10.32,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}化作流星  点亮光明
